<TEXT>
<P>
Does Ruth Reichl think that the San Fernando Valley has seceded from Los 
Angeles? In her listing of her top 40 restaurants, she lists not one single 
restaurant in the Valley. How about The Bistro Garden? Vals in Toluca Lake? 
They're as fine as anything over the hill. 
</P>
<P>
BLANCHE DAVIS 
</P>
<P>
Northridge 
</P>
