a great deal of response from Times' readers. We are grateful for being 
included in your continuing exposure of travel videos. 
</P>
<P>
We also enjoyed Rich Roberts' article, "Drought Is No Deterrent to River 
Rafters So Far," in the same issue. In fact, your entire Travel Section was a 
