Photo, Top Dogs: Bill Watters and his dog, Air Major, seem to be up to the 
competition Saturday at canine Frisbee championships at La Mirada Regional 
Park. More than 50 teams of owners and pets competed in freestyle and distance 
events. Winner and runner-up will be named today. MIKE SERGIEFF / For The Times 
