first day in Moscow. ; Photo, Paul Schrader, right, trades stories with a 
Soviet colleague. ; Photo, John Patrick Shanley: "They want what we can't give 
them." ; Photo, Julius Epstein, left, senior member of the American contingent, 
with Josef Prout, patriarch of Soviet screenwriters. PAMELA FONG; Photo, Anna 
Hamilton Phelan, Lawrence Kasdan and Frank Pierson: glasnostian dialogue. ; 
