REUNIFICATION; ENVIRONMENT; POLLUTION -- WEST GERMANY; LOS ANGELES TIMES POLL; 
ECONOMIST (MAGAZINE); NORTH ATLANTIC TREATY ORGANIZATION; NUCLEAR WEAPONS -- 
GERMANY 
