<P>
GARBAGE COLLECTION RATE INCREASES TO BE CONSIDERED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
LAKEWOOD 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An increase in garbage collection rates will be considered by the City Council 
at its July 10 meeting. 
</P>
<P>
The current rate for once-a-week collection is $7.97 per month. The rate for 
twice-a-week collection is $9.98. If the council approves the increases, the 
rates would jump to $8.49 and $10.64 per month, effective immediately. 
</P>
</TEXT>
